Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 很漂亮的首都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 好像沒什麼生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,本來想讓你們看看我們繁榮的公國
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是現在沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,先去找我父王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,比茲 救援呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 難道你也發病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,父王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 你們願意幫助我們國家和國民嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,人數這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,希婭 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,壞劫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,泛塊浪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,居然會有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,應該夠用一段時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有機會妾身也想試一試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,繆也要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,始？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 剛剛魔眼石好像有點反應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,領主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,汙染調查進度怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,綠洲和流出的河川水質調查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,以及地下水的調查已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不過綠洲水底還沒來得及調查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,綠洲底下埋著什麼古器物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,警備和管理有用到某種古器物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是設在地面上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以那又是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,您幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,還挺靈巧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,始閣下 您這是在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真頑固 那就再來50個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那魔物究竟是什麼 是巴丘拉姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,無所謂 反正汙染的源頭應該就是它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,多半是帶著釋放毒素的固有魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼說的確合情合理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你們能打敗它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,綠洲裡已經沒有魔力反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不過不知道排除了汙染源算不算淨化成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,還是有汙染
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,別這麼洩氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,新鮮的水源會不斷冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,用不了多久綠洲就會恢復如初了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 緹奧說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 那個魔物究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是新的魔物沿著地下水游進來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是魔人族搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,魔人族？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,既然閣下這麼說 想必是有什麼線索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也自主進行了調查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但沒想到有人能驅使如此魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是我們太無知了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我代表國家和國民向你們表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你們拯救了這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好好感謝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不能忘了我這份大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,噢~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,各位聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,綠洲的汙染源已經排除了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然還需要一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們的綠洲很快就會恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 水的儲量也有了保證
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,足夠我們等到救援到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 這邊幾位金級冒險家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,接受了去古盧恩大火山採集靜因石的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,最後幾天 大家振奮精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一起打破這困境吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我留下來治療患者們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,靜因石就拜託你們了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,反正也是順路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我會好好照看繆的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我會加油的 你們一定要平安回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要像剛剛和月姐姐親親一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,和香織姐姐親親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,親了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,原來你看見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,繆也想和爸爸親親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,等繆長大一點再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼一回事 回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,大家是去幹活的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會和月親嘴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣 有這必要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很開心是嗎 把我給忘了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,美味無比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,繆 我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,留在這裡乖乖聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要變成烤兔子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,妾身倒是覺得剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不能被熱得發癢 真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,待會兒把你丟進岩漿裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就是入口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是靜因石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒錯 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,都是些小石子兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,已經被採得差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,想要大豐收
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,得深入到人跡罕至的地方才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,再往前似乎就沒人能活著回來了 別大意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,絕禍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,來玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 讓我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你想試試那個是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 這個新功能威力大得嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,貌似是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,魔力衝擊變換
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,還以為不怎麼樣 沒想到還挺強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,居然還有這樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有了這麼多靜因石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,安卡吉的人們就能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 接下來只要攻略這個大迷宮就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,希婭 心靜自然涼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那些流動的都是水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 好涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 月快壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你倒是挺精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,月 弄點冰出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,腦袋快熱炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真涼快 活過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,放鬆之餘 記得把汗擦擦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,著涼了反應會變遲鈍的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,主人看起來還很輕鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,比不上你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這溫度確實很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,事先準備點冷凍系的古器物就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,連主人都束手無策了就說明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕這就是這大迷宮的主題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,主題？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大迷宮是用來挑戰神的試煉對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那每個大迷宮應該都有各自的主題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,比如奧爾庫斯大迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是與眾多魔物 展開各式各樣的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不斷積累經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,萊森大迷宮則是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,脫離魔力這種強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,鍛鍊應對各種攻擊的反應能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而這個古盧恩大火山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是要克服酷熱對集中注意力的阻礙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在此條件之上鍛鍊應對突襲的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,之前沒仔細想過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,試煉本身 就是解放者們的教導嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,始幫我擦乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有類似的遊樂項目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 又是隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多應該到山腳的高度了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定會出現什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,來翔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來像埋著寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,算上看不見的部分 差不多有百來個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡就是解放者的藏身之所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,按照深度來看應該沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,應該會有最後的守護者 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我們渡過岩漿而來 感覺就像抄了近路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不能認為我們已經通過試煉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,絕禍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,月 我去看看那個島 掩護我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是魔石嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,還要來多少條啊 煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,始 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看來是動真格的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,果然那個島就是終點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直就是在說 要想過此路 先打倒我們再說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 剛剛它們很輕鬆就再生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的有機會打敗它們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕和我們在安卡吉對付的巴丘拉姆魔物一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 身體裡應該有生成岩漿的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是魔石在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,岩漿妨礙我的魔眼確定精準位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不過只能破壞掉那東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這次可不是普通的子彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 像這樣打倒它們就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們也開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,黑玉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,烏拉噠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,魔石的確被擊碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,難道通關條件不是打敗那十條蛇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的寶石是不是碎掉了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,現在擊碎的寶石就有十一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,和我們一起打敗的蛇數量一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,按照寶石的數量擊敗等量的蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說 打倒100條就是通關條件了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼熱的條件下對付100條
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也很切合迷宮的主題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,既然這樣 要做的事情就很簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,久違的一擊了 好好品嘗一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,現在是我領先一步了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 要是妾身打倒的數量最多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,請務必給予妾身獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,光是緹奧大姐可不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要參戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,她們兩個自顧自說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也要兩人世界約會一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,雷龍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,月大人是最強的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,月是個BUG 絕對不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,數量沒增加了 看來這5條就是最後的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,兩條交給妾身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,古盧恩大火山攻略完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 黑與白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:59.71,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:05.71,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:11.05,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:17.47,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:22.89,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:26.65,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:28.48,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:34.41,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:40.37,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:46.08,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:51.51,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:54.76,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:02:00.10,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:12.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:17.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:23.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:29.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:38.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:47.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:52.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:57.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:02.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:07.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:10.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:16.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:21.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:26.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:31.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:12.73,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待的一切皆為虛空一場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:17.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}破滅的希望　虛偽的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:23.93,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嵌入身體的傷口深不見底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:29.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不僅是我　你也背負同樣的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:38.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早已不再奢望　求得誰人原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.82,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕懷中相擁　徒留輪廓難辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:47.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甘願承傷不曾猶豫的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:52.51,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我步履蹣跚　忍痛離開你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:57.49,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:02.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:07.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幾步對錯　令我身負百孔千瘡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:10.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形單影隻漸行漸遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:16.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望碎片　誰人不曾擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:21.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又能作何掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:26.33,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:31.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
